{"tid":16151,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"青年胸襲女途人又揸臀　揭月花$3000上鹹網","createTime":"2016-12-01T10:23:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T14:59:08.000Z","uid":20933,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f50093f5caa25f7fb0b6fa7b36d0fc53b42be0f2","tid":16151,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:23:25.000Z","msg":"一名17歲雙失青年，於今年9月28日晚，在其於沙田白田邨住所附近的行人路上，涉嫌向路過的女途人伸出祿山之爪，揸其臀部，當事主轉身欲與他對質時，他再兩度胸襲事主。被告王森文早前於沙田法院承認控罪，原定今日判刑，但裁判官為被告索取感化報告，把判刑押後至本月15日，期間被告准保釋。 <br />\n<br />\n裁判官庭上向被告律師查問，被告是否經常瀏覽「鹹網」，律師回應指約一星期有兩三次，又透露被告患有讀寫障礙。裁判官之後直接向被告查問，指根據早前索取的報告，被告月花3000港元瀏覽「鹹網」，問被告「係咪刺激啲？」，被告回應指以前瀏覽色情網站是觀看相片，現時看的是影片，不用花錢。 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">裁判官反問被告為何看影片反而不用花費，被告未有正面回應，只表示不會再瀏覽。裁判官謂「你心思思想睇，點算？果啲好吸引」，被告則承諾不會再瀏覽。 </span>"},{"pid":"f1a12cb7ff7bf824a54ce0ec7ec79238485ec429","tid":16151,"uid":10100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:26:05.000Z","msg":"上線啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81e72cfbb47582f10ae6002f2afa1800176a6573","tid":16151,"uid":88,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:28:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5d697a9a0488e9681748ee904b3beba7c95ae6b","tid":16151,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T10:28:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"p